query: WITH entities AS (SELECT customer_id, id FROM deposits WHERE ((customer_id, id) > ($3, $2)) OR $2 IS NULL ORDER BY customer_id, id LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: DepositId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN deposit_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.customer_id, i.id, i.id, e.sequence
